summary: do you think Larry ever broke up? If so, when?
question: do you think Larry ever broke up? If so, when?
answer:
Hey love, I believe they took A break from eachother bc of a fight or stress etc. But I don’t think they took a break with the intention to not get back together; They took a break from eachother, just to relax for a while. I absolutely KNOW FOR SURE that they did note date other men, or hooked up etc.

I believe they took a break around end 2015/2016. Also maybe in 2013. (But again, just to take some time off from eachother). You should understand rhey go through lots of stress; babygate, elouno, hendall etc.

Thank you for the ask, love❤😘
